dct_alternative_sm: Le royaume de Boheme : Carte reduite sur celle de 25 feuilles faite a Prague / par Müller.
dct_description_sm: 1 map : col., mounted on linen ; 50 x 63 cm
Shows parts of Austria, Czechoslovakia, Hungary, Germany and Poland.
Cartouche in upper right hand corner.
Reduced from a map of Bohemia by Johann Christoph Müller, Austrian engineer and cartographer, drawn in 1720 on 25 sheets.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
